data.description: Adorable 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom home with attached carport.  Plenty of shade with the mature trees!  Spacious living room with luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the home.  Laundry is conveniently off the kitchen. Large owner's bedroom.  Nicely updated bathroom with subway tile surrounding the shower.  Large fenced in backyard with a storage shed and another mature tree providing great shade over the patio!
